        "created_at": "2021-01-15T08:10:17.407Z",
        "cooked": "<p>So I just started using Signal and one thing I miss from other video chatting software is the ability to pop out the video of the person you are talking to and placing it on top of websites or other programs. This is particularly helpful when you are watching a movie together.</p>\n<p>I apologize if this is already a feature and I am just not aware of it, but I thought I should make a post at least. Thanks</p>",
