        "id": 109991,
        "name": "",
        "username": "RasperCasper",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/r/ee59a6/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-02-02T17:45:53.599Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I sent a Github request and was informed that the PiP or Picture-inPicture “Mini-Window” is not intended to sit on top of other active applications during a group video call. Please see my link <strong>Github</strong> bug report / feature request.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Desktop/issues/4986#issuecomment-771743276\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Desktop/issues/4986#issuecomment-771743276</a></p>\n<p><strong>Feature Request</strong><br>\nIt would be great if the PiP or “Mini-Window” had the functionality to sit on top of all applications during a video call, allowing users to do other activities while live video feed can be seen in the PIP or “mini-window”.</p>\n<p><strong>Example of a scenario</strong><br>\nA group of us new Signal Desktop users moved from Viber one night to experience the Signal Video Call functionality to play a poker game using the PokerStars desktop application. We enjoy having the ability to do live video calls/meeting during the game, to chat and read poker faces, as you do. My poker playing buddies unfortunately were not impressed with the UI/UX of the PIP or “mini-window” when it came to playing the poker game so we had to revert back to Viber which has this functionality <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/frowning.png?v=12\" title=\":frowning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":frowning:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p><strong>Feature Requests / Issues with PiP:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The PiP or \"mini-window does not pin to the top over the PokerStars program (or any other opened/actively used program) which caused a huff and puff about minimizing and scaling of the PokerStars gaming application windows to allow for the video feed of the Signal PIP to be seen and poker game to be played.</li>\n<li>The PiP of “mini-window” appears to be very small when in mini mode, can this be increased or can the ability to drag a corner to make the mini window larger making it <strong>scalable</strong> .</li>\n<li>On the mini-window, is it possible to have the <strong>Turn off Camera</strong> and <strong>Mute mic</strong> buttons accessible in order to pop out of the room and deal with life’s little issues off camera while the poker game continues as normal for example.</li>\n<li>Again in the “mini-window”, I understand the active speaker gets the spotlight but is it possible to have the ability to pin or select another live player/user via the mini window without the need to go back into main desktop application. It would be cool during silent times to have players live video feeds (not the ones with Camera’s off) rotate and take focus for a couple of seconds then change to next.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>See image of desired list of feature requests. GIMP the image editing application is the background active application.</p>\n<p><strong>Desired use of PiP</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/1/0110a50d66e0ec4dd79b1294a5a220002e241c53.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/0110a50d66e0ec4dd79b1294a5a220002e241c53\" title=\"feature_request_02feb21\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/1/0110a50d66e0ec4dd79b1294a5a220002e241c53_2_625x500.png\" alt=\"feature_request_02feb21\" data-base62-sha1=\"9q8AYJeELmOW2e7rPJd4niTzMv\" width=\"625\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/1/0110a50d66e0ec4dd79b1294a5a220002e241c53_2_625x500.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/1/0110a50d66e0ec4dd79b1294a5a220002e241c53_2_937x750.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/1/0110a50d66e0ec4dd79b1294a5a220002e241c53_2_1250x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"575A5C\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">feature_request_02feb21</span><span class=\"informations\">1280×1024 57.7 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
