        "id": 168639,
        "name": "Glencora Borradaile",
        "username": "glencora-borradaile",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/glencora-borradaile/{size}/28639_2.png",
        "created_at": "2022-02-18T21:50:58.741Z",
        "cooked": "<p>My request was marked as solved by this request, but the requests are different and I don’t know how to reopen it (<a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/have-signal-desktop-open-a-new-window-for-voice-video-calls/41989/2\" class=\"inline-onebox\">Have Signal Desktop open a new window for voice/video calls - #2 by Herohtar</a>)  I was requesting a new window open - not necessarily a hovering window (like a youtube or netflix PiP) which might have fewer features (like screensharing, etc).</p>",
