        "id": 264108,
        "name": "Wyatt Childers",
        "username": "Dark_Arc",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/53a042/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-03-24T17:38:00.246Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Yes, exact same issue … I made a post wanting what you wanted and it was folded into this request.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/pop-out-voice-video-calls-into-a-new-window/67904/4\">https://community.signalusers.org/t/pop-out-voice-video-calls-into-a-new-window/67904/4</a></p>\n<p>I suppose it <em>could</em> be handled the same way, but I’m really not looking for picture-in-picture which is typically a mini-window. I want a full sized window.</p>\n<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/herohtar\">@Herohtar</a></p>",
        "post_number": 10,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 10,
        "updated_at": "2025-03-24T17:38:00.246Z",
